## Disable function usage

- Don't use the function

::: {.cell execution_count=18}
``` {.python .cell-code}
messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "hi!",
    }
]
response = openai.ChatCompletion.create(
    model="gpt-3.5-turbo-0613",
    messages=messages,
    functions=functions,
    function_call="none",
)
print(response)
```
:::


## Force function usage

- force to use the function

::: {.cell execution_count=19}
``` {.python .cell-code}
messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "hi!",
    }
]
response = openai.ChatCompletion.create(
    model="gpt-3.5-turbo-0613",
    messages=messages,
    functions=functions,
    function_call={"name": "get_current_weather"},
)
print(response)
```
:::


## Pass the reults back in the LLM

::: {.cell execution_count=20}
``` {.python .cell-code}
messages = [
    {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "What's the weather like in Boston!",
    }
]
response = openai.ChatCompletion.create(
    model="gpt-3.5-turbo-0613",
    messages=messages,
    functions=functions,
    function_call={"name": "get_current_weather"},
)
print(response)
```
:::


